Write the isClosed method in the NurbsCurve3D class.
Remember to respond with a snippet in the form of the following:
```
class NurbsCurve3D {
    isClosed() {
        // your code here
    }
}
```

```javascript
class NurbsCurve3D {
    isClosed() {
        const firstPoint = this.controlPoints[0];
        const lastPoint = this.controlPoints[this.controlPoints.length - 1];

        return firstPoint.every((coord, index) => coord === lastPoint[index]);
    }
}
```
